Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:02.63,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:05.73,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.46,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:10.37,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today's "MuneDoki" is the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:13.54,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The alibi's just too strong!\NLet your heart beat to the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.47,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's always only one truth!
